**Quality gates**: `bun run lint` · `bun run test` · `bun run ci` · `bun run typecheck` (if present).

**/code-review**: Use code-reviewer; for contracts also solidity-auditor. See [.claude/commands/code-review.md](mdc:.claude/commands/code-review.md).

**/debug**: Reproduce → gather context → analyze logs → test fix. See [.claude/commands/debug.md](mdc:.claude/commands/debug.md).

**/test**: `bun run test`, `bun run test:integration`, `bun run ci`. See [.claude/commands/test.md](mdc:.claude/commands/test.md).

**/pr**: Ensure CI green; semantic commits; create PR and link Linear. See [.claude/commands/pr.md](mdc:.claude/commands/pr.md).

**/setup**: Configure MCP servers (Linear, Context7, DeepWiki, Sentry, Playwright, Gemini, OpenZeppelin). See [.claude/commands/setup.md](mdc:.claude/commands/setup.md).
